{"tid":2458154,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家啲牙醫係咪冇野撈了？","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T04:44:40.000Z","uid":266282,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"436ecbd55df2256e1ce43fe4386296c8b69ab1f2","tid":2458154,"uid":266282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"早果排先興完乜野牙齒美白 條女話拎盞燈照白啲冇乜問題<br />\n我睇果間野好似係IG SHOP咁 又唔係醫生<br />\n不過照一次半次都由佢<br />\n但係佢呢排睇完啲IG廣告又想買個牙箍剩係訓覺帶黎箍牙<br />\n一睇又係冇牙醫剩係買舊野就算<br />\n講到好似夜晚帶朝早唔帶玩幾個月就箍到牙咁<br />\n乜而家連箍牙都唔使牙醫咁L兒戲<br />\n叫佢唔好哂咁多錢信埋哂啲偽醫學野<br />\n實際上貪平嫌煩唔撚睇醫生<br />\n仲夠膽屌我唔識野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我廢 其實都係俾佢屌完係到呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cab369ef1a9d849cf5f0fa20839d725049671ee","tid":2458154,"uid":31521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"去哂唱歌"},{"pid":"a8dcd852caceea2536258257d1c964d4ddfc84a9","tid":2458154,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4818881f80e7f562f0d1ee811a8d520813ec1914","tid":2458154,"uid":431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"整衰啲牙嗰陣唔好嚟診所喊就得"},{"pid":"070b8e8a99b4b3cdeafc6cb883a8efae8d5c5320","tid":2458154,"uid":4064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"叫你女朋友得閒爬下文<br />\nLIHKG 箍牙討論區 38<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2416559\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2416559</a><br />\n<br />\n箍牙POST置頂本身都好多資料防人中伏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GW2T1FYrkVk&amp;ab_channel=Bubebube\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGW2T1FYrkVk%26ab_channel%3DBubebube&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97fzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=1fbd3d7f\" target=\"_blank\">https:/